title: New: Jackie & The Stabbs – I’m Not Waiting
content: If you checked out my Sound of 2012 list, you may recognize the vocals on this track as belonging to a certain Chelsea Burgin, who also lends her fall-head-over-heels-in-love tone and irresistible charm to Columbus five piece Jackie & The Stabbs. I’m Not Waiting is a gorgeous piano ballad, in a similar vein to the likes of Feist and Regina Spektor, with Chelsea’s stunning vocals backed up by an equally bewitching instrumental section.
author: 5e9b68b27a1236eccfeb1d27
